Title: deb-packages: Do not remove /var/lib/check_mk_agent on package update
Level: 2
Edition: cee
Component: agents
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
State: unknown
Version: 1.4.0i1
Date: 1465799884

The Debian packages created by the agent bakery now no longer delete the directory
<tt>/var/lib/check_mk_agent</tt> when the package is <i>updated</i>. It is still
removed when the package is finally uninstalled.
